{"tid":2361988,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於「中國」","createTime":"2021-01-11T06:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T06:31:01.000Z","uid":262677,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2570a657c30b0260c8bdbc13a2309d88f3e0eb9","tid":2361988,"uid":262677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"一有關於「古代中國」嘅po就實有班翰林學士走入去話「民國先有中國呢個term」<br />\n<br />\n《尚書》<br />\n <a href=\"https://ctext.org/shang-shu/timber-of-the-rottlera/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fctext.org%2Fshang-shu%2Ftimber-of-the-rottlera%2Fzh&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7VLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=2ad44e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ctext.org/shang-shu/timber-of-the-rottlera/zh</a><br />\n<br />\n「皇天既付中國民越厥疆土于先王，肆王惟德用，和懌先後迷民，用懌先王受命。」<br />\n<br />\n《尚書正義》<br />\n<a href=\"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&amp;chapter=263434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fctext.org%2Fwiki.pl%3Fif%3Dgb%26chapter%3D263434&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7VLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=6f87eab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&amp;chapter=263434</a><br />\n<br />\n「大天已付周家治中國民矣，能遠拓其界壤，則於先王之道遂大。」<br />\n<br />\n《毛書正義》<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikisource.org/wiki/%E6%AF%9B%E8%A9%A9%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9/%E5%8D%B7%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25AF%259B%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%2F%25E5%258D%25B7%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B8%2583&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7VLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=e696cbd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikisource.org/wiki/%E6%AF%9B%E8%A9%A9%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9/%E5%8D%B7%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%83</a><br />\n<br />\n「民亦勞止，汔可小康。惠此中國，以綏四方。」<br />\n「「中國」之文，與「四方」相對，故知中國謂京師，四方謂諸夏。若以中國對四夷，則諸夏亦為中國。言各有對，故不同也。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8k8tsY4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8k8tsY4.png&h=c7407603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清聖祖實錄卷五十二之部份截圖<br />\n<br />\n《尼布楚條約》<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%B0%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%A5%9A%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%84_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25A5%259A%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25B4%2584_&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7VLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=839dedf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%B0%BC%E5%B8%83%E6%A5%9A%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%84_</a>(%E6%BB%BF%E6%96%87%E6%BC%A2%E8%AD%AF)"}]}